title: Project1
text:
# Calling libraries
library(tidyverse)
library(tidycensus)
library(httr)
library(jsonlite)


## Utilizing Get Function to get information from API
URL <- "https://api.census.gov/data/2004/acs/acs1/pums"
id_info <- httr::GET(URL)
str(id_info, max.level = 1)

List of 10
 $ url        : chr "https://api.census.gov/data/2004/acs/acs1/pums"
 $ status_code: int 200
 $ headers    :List of 12
  ..- attr(*, "class")= chr [1:2] "insensitive" "list"
 $ all_headers:List of 1
 $ cookies    :'data.frame':    1 obs. of  7 variables:
 $ content    : raw [1:3603] 7b 0a 20 20 ...
 $ date       : POSIXct[1:1], format: "2024-09-22 19:50:09"
 $ times      : Named num [1:6] 0 0.00368 0.02106 0.06661 0.08543 ...
  ..- attr(*, "names")= chr [1:6] "redirect" "namelookup" "connect" "pretransfer" ...
 $ request    :List of 7
  ..- attr(*, "class")= chr "request"
 $ handle     :Class 'curl_handle' <externalptr> 
 - attr(*, "class")= chr "response"



## Creating a tibble to view API information
parsed <- fromJSON(rawToChar(id_info$content))
info2 <- as_tibble(parsed$dataset)
info2
